      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel like im stuck in this same shitty cycle over and over. i try to get a job, i mess it up. i try to stay sober, i fail. i try to fix things with people, it just ends the same way. it feels like no matter what i do, i just end up back at zero. i'm just so tired of the loop.",
